  <scopecontent id="aspace_90f6905d240d5733f48cc82b096ae9a8">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains 11 documents, mostly land grants, issued to William Nicoll for land in the Province of New York, relating to the towns of Islip and Huntington in Suffolk County. One document is a court decision issued by Daniel Horsmanden regarding a land dispute between Nicoll and Gilbert Burger.</p>  </scopecontent>
